com.novar.persist

Class JdbcKit

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.novar.persist.JdbcKit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PersistKit

    public class JdbcKit
extends java.lang.Object
implements PersistKit
    This class permit for each method to return the specific Object of the persistence with methods that permit to load, save and more.

    This class implements PersistKit and return the specific Object persistence that you want.
    Author:
    Antoine JOERG, Nicolas PELCE, Othmane EL KOUAHY, Romain GUILMET, Valentin BERCOT-DUFLOS
    See Also:
    PersistKit
